elements.name: As a user, I want to add a new post

steps.name: User is logged to the application
User clicks on New Post menu
User inputs Article title as 'My First Post'
User inputs Article about as 'cypress test'
User input Article description as 'Cypress can do component, api and E2E testing'
User input Article tags as 'cypress, testing'
User clicks on button Publish Article
The new post is published successful
